          <tr>
            <td style="text-align: left; padding: 25px 15px 30px;">
              <span>[10] <a href="https://iarxiv.org/paper/27a2251ba09e1db316deaf84e66c353434d84eaa22263090fcaf9956d4da2c477670c131b73136c710/68747470733a2f2f61727869762e6f72672f6162732f323630342e3134363838">2604.14688</a> (hep-ph) [score: 0.27]</span>
