          <tr>
            <td style="text-align: left; padding: 25px 15px 30px;">
              <span>[19] <a href="https://iarxiv.org/paper/fd83cc4b961ae4ce5cc326a7024aa08b1416b246beff23e11b324749ece3c7d2f9d488025b9aa0a991/68747470733a2f2f61727869762e6f72672f6162732f323630342e3135313130">2604.15110</a> (quant-ph) [score: 0.15]</span>
              <br>
              <span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;"><a href="https://iarxiv.org/paper/c1b762ee05ad32f994a57fb78392d5ea6c2e93781494c35ae895a1065d17fcc9270c0fb28b4c561d85f4/68747470733a2f2f61727869762e6f72672f7064662f323630342e3135313130">         General Static Solutions of the SU(2) Yang-Mills Equations from a Spin Vector Potential
       </a></span>
